originalSql:
WITH UserStats AS (
    SELECT 
        u.Id AS UserId,
        u.DisplayName,
        COUNT(DISTINCT p.Id) AS PostCount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN p.PostTypeId = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS QuestionCount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN p.PostTypeId = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AnswerCount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN v.VoteTypeId = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS UpVotes,
        SUM(CASE WHEN v.VoteTypeId = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DownVotes
    FROM 
        Users u
    LEFT JOIN 
        Posts p ON u.Id = p.OwnerUserId
    LEFT JOIN 
        Votes v ON p.Id = v.PostId
    GROUP BY 
        u.Id, u.DisplayName
),
BadgeCounts AS (
    SELECT 
        b.UserId, 
        COUNT(b.Id) AS BadgeCount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN b.Class = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GoldBadges,
        SUM(CASE WHEN b.Class = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS SilverBadges,
        SUM(CASE WHEN b.Class = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS BronzeBadges
    FROM 
        Badges b
    GROUP BY 
        b.UserId
)
SELECT 
    us.UserId,
    us.DisplayName,
    us.PostCount,
    us.QuestionCount,
    us.AnswerCount,
    COALESCE(bc.BadgeCount, 0) AS TotalBadges,
    COALESCE(bc.GoldBadges, 0) AS GoldBadges,
    COALESCE(bc.SilverBadges, 0) AS SilverBadges,
    COALESCE(bc.BronzeBadges, 0) AS BronzeBadges,
    us.UpVotes,
    us.DownVotes
FROM 
    UserStats us
LEFT JOIN 
    BadgeCounts bc ON us.UserId = bc.UserId
WHERE 
    us.PostCount > 10
ORDER BY 
    us.UpVotes DESC, us.DownVotes ASC
LIMIT 100

SELECT COALESCE("UserId", "UserId") AS "USERID", CASE WHEN CAST("Class" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "FD_COL_1", CASE WHEN CAST("Class" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "FD_COL_2", CASE WHEN CAST("Class" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "FD_COL_3"
FROM "Badges"

SELECT COALESCE("t3"."USERID", "t3"."USERID") AS "USERID", "t3"."DISPLAYNAME", "t3"."POSTCOUNT", "t3"."QUESTIONCOUNT", "t3"."ANSWERCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."BADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."BADGECOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALBADGES", CASE WHEN "t4"."GOLDBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."GOLDBADGES" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "GOLDBADGES", CASE WHEN "t4"."SILVERBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."SILVERBADGES" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "SILVERBADGES", CASE WHEN "t4"."BRONZEBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."BRONZEBADGES" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "BRONZEBADGES", "t3"."UPVOTES", "t3"."DOWNVOTES"
FROM (SELECT MIN("Users"."Id") AS "USERID", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", COUNT(DISTINCT "Posts"."Id") AS "POSTCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Posts"."PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Posts"."PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "ANSWERCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Votes"."VoteTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "UPVOTES", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Votes"."VoteTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "DOWNVOTES"
FROM "Users"
LEFT JOIN "Posts" ON "Users"."Id" = "Posts"."OwnerUserId"
LEFT JOIN "Votes" ON "Posts"."Id" = "Votes"."PostId"
GROUP BY "Users"."Id", "Users"."DisplayName") AS "t3"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "USERID", COUNT(*) AS "BADGECOUNT", SUM("FD_COL_1") AS "GOLDBADGES", SUM("FD_COL_2") AS "SILVERBADGES", SUM("FD_COL_3") AS "BRONZEBADGES"
FROM "s1"
GROUP BY "USERID") AS "t4" ON "t3"."USERID" = "t4"."USERID"
WHERE "t3"."POSTCOUNT" > 10
ORDER BY "t3"."UPVOTES" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t3"."DOWNVOTES"
LIMIT 100
